      View All Reservations
    </a>
  </div> --}}

  <p style="margin-top: 32px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
    Thank you for providing exceptional wine experiences at Rose des Vins!<br>
    Have a wonderful session with your guest. üç∑
  </p>
</div>
